    <metadata>

      <lom xsi:schemaLocation="http://ltsc.ieee.org/xsd/LOM http://ltsc.ieee.org/xsd/lomv1.0/lomLoose.xsd" xmlns="http://ltsc.ieee.org/xsd/LOM">
        <general>
          <identifier>

          </identifier>
          <title>
            <string language="en">Bugscope</string>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Bugscope</string>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Bugscope</string>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">Bugscope</string>
            <string language="x-mt-it">Bugscope</string>
            <string language="x-mt-el">Bugscope</string>
            <string language="x-mt-es">Bugscope</string>
          </title>
          <description>
            <string language="en">offers magnified images of specimens of beetles, spiders, and other insects and anthropoids viewed through an electron microscope.</string>
          </description>
          <keyword>
            <string language="en">Social Sciences</string>
          </keyword>
          <language>en</language>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Angebote vergrößerte Bilder der 
Probenmaterialien der Käfer, der Spinnen und anderer Insekte und 
Anthropoids angesehen durch ein Elektronenmikroskop.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">images magnifiées par offres des spécimens des 
coléoptères, les araignées, et d'autres insectes et anthropoïdes 
visualisés par un microscope électronique.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">imagens ampliadas ofertas dos espécimes dos 
besouros, as aranhas, e os outros insetos e anthropoids vistos 
através de um microscópio de elétron.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-it">immagini ingrandite offerte degli esemplari degli 
scarabei, ragni ed altri insetti ed anthropoids osservati attraverso 
un microscopio elettronico.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-el">προσφέρει τις ενισχυμένες εικόνες των δειγμάτων των 
κανθάρων, των αραχνών, και άλλων εντόμων και anthropoids που 
εμφανίζονται μέσω ενός ηλεκτρονικού μικροσκοπίου.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-es">imágenes magnificadas ofertas de especímenes de 
escarabajos, arañas, y otros insectos y antropoides vistos a través 
de un microscopio electrónico.</string>
          </description>
          <keyword>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Sozialwissenschaften</string>
          </keyword>
          <keyword>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Les Sciences Sociales</string>
          </keyword>

          </keyword>
